Question: Develop an argument for or against using a cellphone while driving.
Answer:
You should not use a cell phone while driving.  if your paying attention to your phone then your not paying full attention to the road, or the 2 ton death trap your driving on it.  If your not paying full attention then its a lot easier to get into a car crash and hurt not only yourself but someone else.  Studies have shown that driving while using a cell phone can be just as bad as driving intoxicated.